snippet.title: Black Ops 6 - Gameplay Reveal Trailer
snippet.description:
Forced to go rogue. Hunted from within. This is Call of Duty #BlackOps6

💥 All-new campaign set in the Gulf War era 
🗺️ 12 new 6v6 maps & 4 new strike maps at launch 
🧟 Return of Round-based Zombies 

Pre-Order to instantly get the Woods Operator Pack 👉 https://a.atvi.com/PreOrderBO6

Follow #CallofDuty for the latest intel:
• X / (Formerly Twitter): http://twitter.com/CallofDuty
